+.TH mod\-ui\-launcher 1 2023-03-01 mod-ui "The mod-ui web interface"
+.SH About
+.PP
+mod\-ui\-launcher is an utility script which launches all the required daemons for the
+mod-devices mod-ui interface
+.PP
+Currently the launcher will:
+.RS
+.IP \(bu 2
+Open a progress dialog
+.IP \(bu 2
+Start jackd using the arguments found in $JACKD_ARGS, or typical arguments if $JACKD_ARGS
+is empty
+.IP \(bu 2
+Start mod-host with typical arguments
+.IP \(bu 2
+jack_load mod-monitor
+.IP \(bu 2
+Start the mod-ui webserver on port 8888
+.IP \(bu 2
+Open your preferred web browser to http://localhost:8888
+.RE
+.PP
+mod\-ui\-launcher is part of the MOD audio project
+\[la]https://mod.audio/about\[ra]\&.
+.SH Features
+.PP
+mod\-ui\-launcher has very basic error checking and will tear down all its own daemons
+upon exit.
+This was chosen in preference to checking whether jackd or mod-host are already running
+to let you easier start from a blank slate when testing your $JACKD_ARGS.
+.SH "SEE ALSO"
